Package gal4j.algorithm

Class Engine

java.lang.Object
gal4j.algorithm.Engine
public class Engine extends Object
Engine is the core class that runs the genetic algorithm process. It manages population initialization, fitness evaluation, selection, crossover, mutation, and termination based on configuration and operators.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Filip KÅ™enek

      public boolean checkEndConditions()
      Checks whether the end conditions for the algorithm have been met.
